parameters:
\SE[16]I-I've come back...! \!\SE[11]If things continue like
this, what will happen...!?

\SE[52]In the morning, I wake up and can't remember my dreams
anymore. \SE[38]Maybe, all of them...

\SE[64] I wonder if I can escape with 'magic'...!? Like those
girls...!

\SE[37]I used up all my magic to surprise that child...
\!\SE[52]Actually, I'm empty inside...
\SE[64]I-Is that so...!? \SE[60]If I did all that, I see...!

\SE[2]How did Laura manage to enter my dreams? \!\SE[13]If I
could exit using the same method...

\SE[16]Uunagi-chan!! If you can hear me, please help us!!
\!\SE[52]We are here!!

\SE[52]Because this is the deepest part of my heart, my voice
might not reach others... \SE[38]It's a distance that would take
several months to walk normally...
